# ✈️ Flight Price Prediction

A large-scale dataset of **300,153 flight records** across Indian domestic routes,
designed for exploring price prediction, feature engineering, and travel pattern analysis.

## 📦 Dataset Overview

| Column | Description |
|---|---|
| `airline` | Name of the airline carrier |
| `source_city` | City of departure |
| `destination_city` | City of arrival |
| `departure_time` | Time slot of departure (Morning, Evening, etc.) |
| `arrival_time` | Time slot of arrival |
| `stops` | Number of stops (zero, one, two_or_more) |
| `class` | Seat class (Economy / Business) |
| `duration` | Total flight duration (in hours) |
| `days_left` | Days remaining before departure |
| `price` | 🎯 Target — ticket price in INR |

## 🔍 Project Scope

- **EDA** — Price distributions, route analysis, airline patterns
- **Feature Engineering** — Encoding, chi-square tests, correlation
- **Modelling** — Regression to predict flight ticket price

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

`Python` · `Pandas` · `Scikit-learn` · `Matplotlib` · `Seaborn` · `SciPy`
